WEBVTT

34:01.609 --> 34:04.192
For the first time
when I committed a murder...

34:04.275 --> 34:05.984
and saw the blood...

34:06.525 --> 34:09.609
I realised that it is the cure
for my disease.

34:11.192 --> 34:14.817
After the shivering stopped, my hands
were urging me to paint something.

34:14.942 --> 34:17.234
So I painted by dead father.

34:23.025 --> 34:24.567
My father's death...

34:25.275 --> 34:29.150
marked the birth of a great painter
called Pattampoochi.

34:29.900 --> 34:32.984
400 years after Caravaggio,
